modName: 3 ECE presets and exported heads for RaceMenu.
summary: Just a three ECE presets and 3 head meshes to import via RaceMenu.
descriptionHtml:
Not much to write about. It is just a three ECE presets. It is more or less a conversion of my presets from Race Menu.

If you would like to achieve the same effect as on screenshot then use:

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/51602/?]Fair Skin Textures.[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12951/?]Enhanced Character Edit[/url] with the [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/35713/?]Enhancer[/url]
SG Hairs or [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/68311/?]KS Hairdos[/url]
[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?]Eyes of Beauty[/url]
